::Shadow Wing::

Her wings were folded up under her and losing feeling. Her leg was 
being pressed against a tooth and slowly getting cut.  She was 
twisted around and losing feeling in her legs and wings.  She beat 
around inside the cats mouth. She slammed her fist into a tooth and 
screetched as she almost broke her hand. All she could so was hope 
that the tiger didn't swallow her.
